{"tid":1836951,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE下月中恢復正常活動 具體日程容後公佈","createTime":"2020-01-23T11:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T11:49:42.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c49f670cf59a39975367267db870ba2a1ced2054","tid":1836951,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"粉絲等好耐嘅好消息！<br />\n<br />\n上年IZ*ONE因爲《Produce 101》系列造假關係被逼全面暫停活動，連原本即將推出的新專輯也無奈叫停。一時間網上充滿各種輿論，甚至有網民要求組合解散，加上案件仍未查明，種種不明朗讓IZ*ONE一度陷入危機。造假案目前已經進入司法程序，組合亦是時候決定未來的安排。幸好在成員各自經紀公司與Mnet方面多番商議後，達成恢復活動的協議，早前宣佈最快在月内推出被延遲的新專。<br />\n<br />\n今日Mnet方面終於正式發表官方立場，首先感謝一直等待IZ*ONE回歸的粉絲，經過多方的討論後大家都決定尊重成員和粉絲想要正常活動的願望，決定將會在2月重新開展行程，具體日程會在之後公佈。Mnet希望大家可以給予成員更多溫暖的支持，因爲她們都是受害者，在這段時間内心也備受煎熬。<br />\n<br />\n最後Mnet強調事件並不是出道藝人、練習生或所屬公司的錯，願類似事件不要再發生，讓大家再受傷。粉絲對IZ*ONE恢復活動大多表示歡迎，但質疑的聲音依然存在，因爲直到現在可以肯定造假的確存在，但卻一直沒有公佈真實的排名，所以並不能說所有成員都是無辜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5789730-izone%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E5%85%B7%E9%AB%94%E6%97%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%B9%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88?current_cat=119360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5789730-izone%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2581%25A2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%2585%25B7%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588%3Fcurrent_cat%3D119360&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=ad4479f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5789730-izone%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E5%85%B7%E9%AB%94%E6%97%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%B9%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88?current_cat=119360</a>"},{"pid":"a9f5a650deb0e40a72c852ffb2e0c688953a1106","tid":1836951,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"IZ*ONE=受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/bee300c7a4946f8b3d4a73cca528c84b/2bd23ae5d2092e7d-35/s400x600/807c72d585853862940a7464b0f7120dcf7ce26b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fbee300c7a4946f8b3d4a73cca528c84b%2F2bd23ae5d2092e7d-35%2Fs400x600%2F807c72d585853862940a7464b0f7120dcf7ce26b.gif&h=826e6a2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dcb25c40818f65df544178af0fb1f4ebbdc7c82","tid":1836951,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"真係慘 俾公司mnet 同啲fans 推番出嚟俾人瘋狂恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}